summary: The caller wants to speak with someone who can provide information about becoming a distributor of ITC products. Initially, the caller is frustrated because he is unable to communicate in Tamil, which he would like, and is transferred multiple times. Eventually, he is connected with a representative named Kandippa who is based in Bangalore but can help the caller. The caller provides his contact information and location, and Kandippa assures the caller that he will register the request and that a team will be in contact with him regarding next steps. The caller also inquires about cigarettes, and Kandippa confirms that ITC is a distributor of cigarettes as well as several other types of products. The call ends with both parties thanking each other.
speaker_a_summary: The speaker is calling from Trichy to a Tamil-speaking person in Sri Venkateswara Store to inquire about being a distributor for their products. They are also trying to get a contact number for a dealer in Herod. The call gets cut off and the speaker tries to get the other person's name and a way to contact them. The call ends without any conclusions being made.
speaker_b_summary: The customer calls R T C to change the language of the call to Tamil and wants to speak to the owner of the store. The owner of the store is called Venkateswara Store and they are located at 1130, 208 Ramaswamy Plaza, Shankar Shankar Street, Sangaringala, Saranga Sar, Trichengodu, THIRUCHUNGODU. The customer wants to know how to get supply for their store and wants to know the details of the products, pricing, discounts and where the team is going to contact them from. The call center agent tells them that they will need to provide their PIN code to proceed but the customer does not provide this information. The call center agent then tells the customer that they will need to register the request in order for the team to contact them and provide the necessary information. The customer also wants to know if they can get cigarettes and IC products for all products and the call center agent tells them that they can adjust all the items for the customer. They also provide their contact number for the customer to call back and then thank the customer for calling.
cohere_points:
- Customer is calling in to register a request for a product from ITC, specifically cigarettes and wants to know where they would need to go to get them. 
- They will need to provide their PIN code, contact number and address for delivery. 
- Agent will register the request and confirm with the customer soon. 
- The customer's name is John. 
- Agent is fromRTC and is located in Bangalore.
